✅ Method 1: Use Valid_If (Best & Easy)
Go to your Phone column → set this formula in Valid_If:

COUNT(
  SELECT(
    YourTableName[Phone],
    [Phone] = [_THIS]
  )
) = 0
---------------------------

💡 Better (recommended AppSheet pattern)

Instead of COUNT, use ISBLANK() for cleaner validation:
ISBLANK(
  SELECT(
    Appointment[Phone_No],
    AND(
      [Phone_No] = [_THIS],
      [Uinique_ID] <> [_THISROW].[Uinique_ID]
    )
  )
)

🧠 Why this works
[_THISROW].[Appointment_ID] = current row being edited
<> excludes itself from duplicate check
So:
Add → checks all rows
Edit → ignores itself, checks others only





  
